headline: CoStar (NASDAQ:CSGP) Posts Better-Than-Expected Sales In Q3
summary: Real estate data provider CoStar Group (NASDAQ:CSGP) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 20.4% year on year to $833.6 million. On top of that, next quarter’s revenue guidance ($890 million at the midpoint) was surprisingly good and 3.3% above what analysts were expecting. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.23 per share was 21.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: CoStar Group Q3 Revenue Increases 20% Year-over-Year, Net New Bookings up 92% Year-over-Year to $84 Million
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., October 28, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, announced today that revenue for the quarter ended September 30, 2025 was $834 million, up 20% over revenue of $693 million for the quarter ended September 30, 2024.
